'''Aola''' was a type of cooking oil commonly found on the planet, [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. Stored at room temperature, its culinary value was ideal for basting roasts such as [[Bantha rump]]. The chef [[Gormaanda/Legends|Gormaanda]], provided instructional [[Holovid/Legends|holovids]] including tips on how to properly use this food additive for various meals. Shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]], [[Mallatobuck/Legends|Mallatobuck]], used liberal helpings of this item when preparing a special [[Life Day/Legends|Life Day]] [[Bantha rump|Bantha surprise]] dinner for her husband, [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]]. [[Fried Endorian chicken]] was fried in Aola and then served.

{{Food-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
In the Star Wars Holiday Special, Cooking Oil was used as Aola. (Script only)

